work.work-title: Lord, grant us, like the watching five

credit.credit-words: May we not wait in selfish sloth, But mingle prayer and work, that both May trim the shining light; So from the midnight of their sin May many, with us, enter in, To banquet in Thy sight.
Lord, grant us, like the watching five

direction-type.words: Lord, grant us, like the watching
Each one her lamp to trim;
And, since the oil Thou dost
the lost, the sick, the lone,
